{"tid":1883760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱栢康有份】原來台灣翻拍左荃灣石棺藏屍案做電影","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T07:36:13.000Z","uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8369651d3d77ef95df0b42eb4a6c128cb25c6dcb","tid":1883760,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/article/538998-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%90%88%E6%8B%8D%E3%80%8A%E5%A4%B1%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8B-%E6%94%B9%E7%B7%A8%E8%87%AA%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%9F%B3%E6%A3%BA%E8%97%8F%E5%B1%8D%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Farticle%2F538998-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%258B%258D%25E3%2580%258A%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258B-%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25A3%25BA%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25B1%258D%25E6%25A1%2588&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=49b87386\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.upower.com.hk/article/538998-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%90%88%E6%8B%8D%E3%80%8A%E5%A4%B1%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8B-%E6%94%B9%E7%B7%A8%E8%87%AA%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%9F%B3%E6%A3%BA%E8%97%8F%E5%B1%8D%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2020/02/20200213_en_%E5%A4%B1%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA-2-e1581590259790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2020%2F02%2F20200213_en_%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-2-e1581590259790.jpg&h=bb92ea27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7aEN5iWMatg&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7aEN5iWMatg%26feature%3Demb_title&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=4e9aaed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7aEN5iWMatg&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n台港合拍《失路人》 改編自荃灣石棺藏屍案 <br />\n<br />\n台灣電影《失路人》改編香港石棺藏屍案，電影由台港兩地合拍，由《陽光普照》陳以文、金都》的朱栢康、《比悲傷更悲傷的故事》石知田、黃采儀等人主演。<br />\n<br />\n電影講述臺仔與阿聰、Panda於香港合租某工廈的一個單位，阿聰欠業主波士十萬，同一時間波士卻垂涎Panda美色，臺仔因心儀Panda而勒索波士，眾人墮詭異的四角關係。波士卻以為是阿聰勒索自己，上門談判時卻被阿聰錯手殺害，三人因走投無路而到逃亡到台灣。臺仔的父母愛子心切而捲入這場危機。三個異鄉人展開台港逃亡之旅。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n但香港上映無期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人都去唔到臺灣"}]}